3527	  be such that \(D(r) \le q.X_i\) for some member of the cover (as produced by
3528	  \cref{lem:exists_finite_basicOpen_cover_le_quasicoherentData}). Then the restricted counit is an
3529	  isomorphism,
3530	  \[
3531	    \mathrm{IsIso}\bigl((M|_{D(r)}).\mathrm{fromTildeΓ}\bigr),
3532	  \]
3533	  i.e. \(M|_{D(r)}\) is identified with the tilde \(\widetilde{N}\) of the \(R_r\)-module
3534	  \(N = \Gamma(M, D(r))\) on \(\Spec R_r \cong D(r)\).
